<section class="what-is-this">
  <%= image_tag image_url("landing/weekend/top-divider.svg"), class: "what-is-this__divider", alt: "", aria: { hidden: true }, loading: "lazy" %>
  <%= image_tag image_url("landing/space/moon-opp.png"), class: "what-is-this__moon", alt: "", aria: { hidden: true }, loading: "lazy" %>
  <div class="what-is-this__card-stack">
    <div class="what-is-this__border what-is-this__border--1">
      <div class="what-is-this__border what-is-this__border--2">
        <div class="what-is-this__border what-is-this__border--3">
          <div class="what-is-this__border what-is-this__border--4">
            <div class="what-is-this__inner">
              <h2 class="what-is-this__title">What <span class="what-is-this__title--italic">is</span> this?</h2>
              <div class="what-is-this__body">
                <p>Stardance Challenge is a <strong>free summer STEM event</strong> where you can make any software/hardware project you want, and get rewarded for it!</p>
                <p>We&rsquo;re a team of teenagers from Hack Club, a nonprofit that&rsquo;s shipped 12,000 prizes to teen makers across 119 countries.</p>
                <p>There&rsquo;ll be new content, freebies, AMAs with astronauts, and other awesome stuff from June 1st to September 30th.</p>
                <p>You don&rsquo;t need experience &mdash; we have guides to help you get started, and a community of teens building alongside you. If you have an idea, that&rsquo;s enough.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="what-is-this__footnote">
      Curious about Hack Club? Learn more about
      <a href="https://hackclub.com/philanthropy/">our donors</a>
      or
      <a href="https://hackclub.com/">other programs</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
